<plot>Marie has a very busy father. Walking in the town, he meets people in every corner, and little Marie gets bored listening to adults talk. To make her point, she decides to climb to the round tower. But when daddy still doesn't notice her disappearance, she has to find other ways to express herself. The burst of anger is needed to make the girl and her father to understand each other.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?336726</url></doc>
